"title": "2426: gospel, responses to",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2426: gospel, responses to",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The gospel cannot be subscribed to half-heartedly or in part; it must be either accepted or rejected.</p>\n<h2>The gospel calls for a positive response</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:5-Rom10:13\">ROM 10:5–10:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:38-Acts13:39\">ACT 13:38–13:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:29-Acts16:32\">ACT 16:29–16:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:21-Rom3:26\">ROM 3:21–3:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:41-John6:52\">JHN 6:41–6:52</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:1\">1JN 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:5\">1JN 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:10-1John5:12\">1JN 5:10–5:12</a></p>\n<h2>The command to accept the gospel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:28\">MAT 11:28</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:30\">ACT 17:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:19-Matt6:24\">MAT 6:19–6:24</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:34-Luke11:36\">LUK 11:34–11:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:7-Matt7:12\">MAT 7:7–7:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:9-Luke11:13\">LUK 11:9–11:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:24-Matt7:27\">MAT 7:24–7:27</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:47-Luke6:49\">LUK 6:47–6:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:13-John4:14\">JHN 4:13–4:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:35-John6:40\">JHN 6:35–6:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:31-John8:32\">JHN 8:31–8:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:36\">JHN 8:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:9-John10:10\">JHN 10:9–10:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:25-John11:26\">JHN 11:25–11:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:44-John12:46\">JHN 12:44–12:46</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of people who accepted the gospel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:16-Mark1:18\">MRK 1:16–1:18</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:18-Matt4:22\">MAT 4:18–4:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:19-Mark1:20\">MRK 1:19–1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:9\">MAT 9:9</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:14\">MRK 2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:27-Luke5:28\">LUK 5:27–5:28</a> <em>Matthew was also known as Levi</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:41\">ACT 2:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:19-Acts11:21\">ACT 11:19–11:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:46-Acts13:48\">ACT 13:46–13:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:13-Acts16:15\">ACT 16:13–16:15</a></p>\n<h2>Rejection of the gospel</h2>\n<h3>Through lack of perception</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:37-John12:41\">JHN 12:37–12:41</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:13-Matt13:15\">MAT 13:13–13:15</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:10-Mark4:12\">MRK 4:10–4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:9-Luke8:10\">LUK 8:9–8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:9\">ISA 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:8\">ROM 11:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:17-Eph4:19\">EPH 4:17–4:19</a></p>\n<h3>Through worldly distractions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:22\">MAT 13:22</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:18-Mark4:19\">MRK 4:18–4:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:14\">LUK 8:14</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:24\">MAT 6:24</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:13\">LUK 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:10\">2TI 4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:4\">JAS 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:15\">1JN 2:15</a></p>\n<h3>Through indifference</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:30\">MAT 12:30</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:23\">LUK 11:23</a></p>\n<h3>Through hostility to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:6-Rom8:8\">ROM 8:6–8:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:13-John7:20\">JHN 7:13–7:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:24-John10:33\">JHN 10:24–10:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:15-Acts4:18\">ACT 4:15–4:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:17-Acts5:28\">ACT 5:17–5:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:51-Acts7:53\">ACT 7:51–7:53</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:8-Acts19:9\">ACT 19:8–19:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:27-Acts21:32\">ACT 21:27–21:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:14-1Thess2:16\">1TH 2:14–2:16</a></p>\n<h2>Warnings against rejecting the gospel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:1-Heb2:4\">HEB 2:1–2:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:36-Mark8:38\">MRK 8:36–8:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:5\">LUK 12:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:16-Luke12:21\">LUK 12:16–12:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:22-Luke13:30\">LUK 13:22–13:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:47-John12:50\">JHN 12:47–12:50</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:4-Heb6:6\">HEB 6:4–6:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:29-Heb10:31\">HEB 10:29–10:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:25\">HEB 12:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:17-2Pet2:22\">2PE 2:17–2:22</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of people who rejected the gospel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:16-Matt19:22\">MAT 19:16–19:22</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:17-Mark10:22\">MRK 10:17–10:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:18-Luke18:23\">LUK 18:18–18:23</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:29-Acts5:33\">ACT 5:29–5:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:51-Acts7:58\">ACT 7:51–7:58</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:32\">ACT 17:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:44-Acts13:47\">ACT 13:44–13:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:23-Acts19:28\">ACT 19:23–19:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:24-Acts24:25\">ACT 24:24–24:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:24-Acts26:28\">ACT 26:24–26:28</a></p>\n<h2>The gospel evokes opposition</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:14\">JHN 17:14</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:13\">ACT 17:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:8\">ACT 13:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:5-Acts17:9\">ACT 17:5–17:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:14-1Thess2:16\">1TH 2:14–2:16</a></p>\n<h2>The gospel evokes persecution</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:1-Acts8:3\">ACT 8:1–8:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:7\">1TH 3:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:49-Acts13:50\">ACT 13:49–13:50</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:4\">2TH 1:4</a></p>",
